/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 希望可以養肥返佢"},{"pid":"74929586dd077b7e8db1c33d574cf8af54a5ad69","tid":301521,"uid":9574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T23:49:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有冇守宮係唔洗餵昆蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申一直想養但好撚驚蟲</blockquote><br />\n睇睇下就慣</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 話雖如此，好難想像我會養一大兜蟲係屋企，諗都唔敢諗"},{"pid":"0ea07073671aa47baf3d3ea8fadb1ad95ef596f9","tid":301521,"uid":9362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T00:55:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有冇守宮係唔洗餵昆蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申一直想養但好撚驚蟲</blockquote><br />\n睇睇下就慣</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 話雖如此，好難想像我會養一大兜蟲係屋企，諗都唔敢諗</blockquote><br />\n可以餵果泥，有d有加蟲粉，唔一定要餵生蟲"},{"pid":"a9a146f122f44b2889c5336c8419c5b4ae13c44b","tid":301521,"uid":68953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T04:30:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主可唔可以update 下，好少見咁瘦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 希望可以養肥返佢</blockquote><br />\n前排日日逼佢食果泥，肥左啲，但依個星期冇逼，瘦返<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f85321a46fbbd39b82e3411ad9688eb99320ab07","tid":301521,"uid":56162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T07:05:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓主可唔可以update 下，好少見咁瘦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 希望可以養肥返佢</blockquote><br />\n前排日日逼佢食果泥，肥左啲，但依個星期冇逼，瘦返<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n😂😂<br />\n佢係咪唔鐘意食野架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n諗起我個兩隻初初買番黎都唔食野。 餓佢一兩日之後差d個鉗都俾佢咬爆 勁狼胎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自此長期食蟲都無問題"},{"pid":"60a5accc36621a42567f181e2ff822e2ec550b2b","tid":301521,"uid":56162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T07:07:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有冇守宮係唔洗餵昆蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申一直想養但好撚驚蟲</blockquote><br />\n睇睇下就慣</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 話雖如此，好難想像我會養一大兜蟲係屋企，諗都唔敢諗</blockquote><br />\n到日又買左一大兜 其實喂蟲都係一種玩法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n放d野落去 幾個鐘後就食哂 覺得好神奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04ef43fd19b1dfee942c5743b89a89b14b67bd21","tid":301521,"uid":38401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T11:11:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/10/190820_a749f1745bd7fa7466f3b1438ff31db7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F10%2F190820_a749f1745bd7fa7466f3b1438ff31db7.jpg&h=7535dfcc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n留名 我隻睫角b唔鐘意食果泥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n次次食兩啖就擰歪面 依家日日跟蟀毛"},{"pid":"b00099916a038727465aa27ff5f155eda0dc5277","tid":301521,"uid":56162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T11:19:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/10/190820_a749f1745bd7fa7466f3b1438ff31db7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F10%2F190820_a749f1745bd7fa7466f3b1438ff31db7.jpg&h=7535dfcc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n留名 我隻睫角b唔鐘意食果泥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n次次食兩啖就擰歪面 依家日日跟蟀毛</blockquote><br />\n好似無坐低浸泥漿浴咋<img src=\"/assets/faces